svg.title: System Sequence Diagram: US04 - Create a Scenario

g.text: System Sequence Diagram: US04 - Create a Scenario
shows map list and asks to select one
requests name, start and end date (time period)
shows list of industries in the map and asks to select the ones available
selects the available industries in the scenario
[for each port (mixed industry) in the select industries]
shows a list of cargoes and asks to select the ones the port imports
selects the cargoes the port imports
asks to select the ones the port exports
selects the cargoes the port exports
asks to select the cargoes the port produces
selects the cargoes the port produces
[for each generating industry (primary) in the select industries]
[for each city in the selected map]
requests the traffic rate for mail and passengers
types the traffic rate for mail and passengers
shows a list of locomotive types and asks to select the available ones
shows all data and requests confirmation
